  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-4193c6b7e976",
  "content": "### 1. Broken cross-file import resolution (D72)\n### 2. Markdown chunks have zero relations (D73)\n\n### 3. No declaration→usage tracking across files (D74)\n\nWhen `QueryableStore` is defined in `traits.rs` and used in `lite_store.rs`, `knowledge_store.rs`, and `postgres_store.rs`, there are no edges connecting them. The only cross-file relation type is `imports`, which is broken (see #1).\n\n---\n",
